CEDURE [TTY.Handle];  WriteUniversalID: PROCEDURE [TTY.Handle, System.UniversalID];  WriteVolumeID: PROCEDURE [TTY.Handle, Volume.ID];  END.LOGAugust 11, 1980 9:43 PM   SXY      Add DefaultWindow: TTY.Handle and TTY. Convert from Command to TTYCommand.September 8, 1980  1:29 PM   SXY      Added TTY.Handle as a parameter. DefaultWindow is corrected to defaultWindow.October 1, 1980  1:57 PM   AWL         Added various procedures to deal with physical volumes and devices.  Added procedures to convert between UID's and String's. 2-Sep-81 15:16:45   WDK       LONGified. 6-Jan-83 17:46:37   EKN       Updated to Klamath: changed File.Capabilities to File.File, changed Space.Handle to Space.Interval, deleted WritePermissions.  Changed GetDeviceCur to not return device type.  Changed SetDeviceCur to not take device type.  Added currentPhysicalVolumeID.